{"lemma":"صِبْغَةُ","slug":"صِبْغَةُ","root":"ص.ب.غ","root_slug":"ص-ب-غ","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ب-غ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"صِبْغَة","root":"صبغ","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23709","n23716","n23717"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%92%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"dye, colorant"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"tinge, a colour created by (or as if created by) dyeing"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the art of dyeing"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sˤib.ɣa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23709","headword_ar":"صَبَغَهُ","root":"Sbg","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K, the former not in the copy of the K used by SM) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, O, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabogN","text_ar":"صَبْغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SibagN","text_ar":"صِبَغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, O, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SibagapN","text_ar":"صِبَغَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AHn, TA,) [of which last,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SibogapN","text_ar":"صِبْغَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.), also said to be an inf. n., is perhaps a contraction, or, as is said in the Ksh ii. 132, it means a mode, or manner, of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabog","text_ar":"صَبْغ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He dyed it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coloured it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K TA;) namely, a garment, or piece of cloth; (S, O, Msb, TA;) and white, or hoary, hair, and the like. (TA.) [It is said that] the primary meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~abogu","text_ar":"الصَّبْغُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the language of the Arabs is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The altering"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a thing]: and hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Subiga Alv~awobu","text_ar":"صُبِغَ الثَّوْبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth, was altered in colour"},{"kind":"text","text":"to blackness or redness or yellowness [&c.]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabaga All~uqomapa","text_ar":"صَبَغَ اللُّقْمَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabogN","text_ar":"صَبْغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He moistened the mouthful with oil"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grease"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any kind of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sibog","text_ar":"صِبْغ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sauce"},{"kind":"text","text":"& c.]; and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he dipped it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"immersed it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner any other thing. (TA.) [Thus] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabaga","text_ar":"صَبَغَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yadahu biAlmaA='i","text_ar":"يَدَهُ بِالمَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, O, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlmaA='i","text_ar":"فِى المَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He dipped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"immersed, his hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arm, in the water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, O, K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabagati Aln~aAqapu","text_ar":"صَبَغَتِ النَّاقَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aAfirahaA fiY AlmaA='i","text_ar":"مَشَافِرَهَا فِى المَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, O) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlmaA='i","text_ar":"بِالمَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The she-camel dipped her lips in the water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, O, TA.) ―         -b3-  [Hence also,] the term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabogN","text_ar":"صَبْغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used by the Christians as meaning (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dipping,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"immersing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of their children, [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"baptizing"},{"kind":"text","text":"them,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, S, * TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabaga waladahu","text_ar":"صَبَغَ وَلَدَهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Aln~aSoraAniy~api","text_ar":"فِى النَّصْرَانِيَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabogN","text_ar":"صَبْغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(as shown in the next preceding sentence) and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SibogapN","text_ar":"صِبْغَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He introduced his child into the Christian communion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is said,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by dipping,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"immersing, him in the water of baptism."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabaga waladahu fiY Alyahuwdiy~api","text_ar":"صَبَغَ وَلَدَهُ فِى اليَهُودِيَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He introduced his child into the Jewish communion"},{"kind":"text","text":"[probably"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by baptism combined with circumcision:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SibogapN","text_ar":"صِبْغَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", an explanation of which seems to indicated that circumcision alone is meant in this case]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaSobuguwna AlHadiyva","text_ar":"يَصْبُغُونَ الحَدِيثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They colour and alter information,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discourse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabaguwhu fiY Eayonihi","text_ar":"صَبَغُوهُ فِى عَيْنِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They altered him in his estimation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"informed him that he had become altered from the state in which he was."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And it is said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaguwniY fiY Eayonika","text_ar":"صَبَغُونِى فِى عَيْنِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaguwniY","text_ar":"صَبَغُونِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Einodaka","text_ar":"عِنْدَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They pointed me out to thee as one who would accomplish what thou desiredst of me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"from the saying of the Arabs,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabagotu Alr~ajula biEayoniY","text_ar":"صَبَغْتُ الرَّجُلَ بِعَيْنِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biyadiY","text_ar":"بِيَدِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I pointed at the man with my eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with my hand:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K: *) but Az says that this is a mistake; that the Arabs when they mean thus say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaEotu","text_ar":"صَبَعْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with the unpointed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E","text_ar":"ع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.) ―         -b6-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabaga yadahu biAlEilomi","text_ar":"صَبَغَ يَدَهُ بِالعِلْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bifan~K mina","text_ar":"بِفَنٍّ مِنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEilomi","text_ar":"العِلْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlEamali","text_ar":"بِالعَمَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He laboured in science,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a species of science"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knowledge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in work,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and became notable therein"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereby"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabaga DaroEuhaA","text_ar":"صَبَغَ ضَرْعُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SubuwgN","text_ar":"صُبُوغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Her udder became full, and goodly in colour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA:) said of a camel. (O, TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabagato EaDalatuhu","text_ar":"صَبَغَتْ عَضَلَتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SubuwgN","text_ar":"صُبُوغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) said of a man, (O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EDlp","text_ar":"عضلة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"muscle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became long:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabagato","text_ar":"سَبَغَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabaga Alv~awobu","text_ar":"صَبَغَ الثَّوْبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SubuwgN","text_ar":"صُبُوغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth, was long and ample:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaga","text_ar":"سَبَغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabaga fiY AlT~aEaAmi","text_ar":"صَبَغَ فِى الطَّعَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. a camel]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put his head into the food:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaA^a","text_ar":"صَبَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabagati AlA_ibilu fiY Alr~iEoYi","text_ar":"صَبَغَتِ الاـِبِلُ فِى الرِّعْىِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels put their heads into the pasture,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabagato fiyhaA raA^osahaA","text_ar":"صَبَغَتْ فِيهَا رَاْسَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi","text_ar":"فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She put her head into it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaA^ato","text_ar":"صَبَاَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Fr","O","Msb","K","S","As","AHn","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n23716","headword_ar":"صُبْغَةٌ","root":"Sbg","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", in a sheep or goat, or in a ewe, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whiteness of the extremity of the tail;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the quality denoted by the epithet"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabogaA='u","text_ar":"صَبْغَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A date that has become partly ripe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ripe in a part thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n23717","headword_ar":"صِبْغَةٌ","root":"Sbg","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SibogN","text_ar":"صِبْغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence. ―         -b2-  It also means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Religion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diyn","text_ar":"دِين"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AA, O, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mil~ap","text_ar":"مِلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"religious law,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ariyEap","text_ar":"شَرِيعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything whereby one advances himself in the favour of God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, TA:) [thus,] in the Kur [ii. 132], (O, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sibogapa A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"صِبْغَةَ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the religion of God,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiTorapa A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"فِطْرَةَ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diyna A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"دِينَ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) which is the meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiTorapa A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"فِطْرَةَ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the religion of God, with an adaptation to which mankind are created;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because its effect appears in him who has it like the dye in the garment; (Bd, Jel;) or because it intermingles in the heart like the dye in the garment; (Bd;) and it is said to be from the Christians'"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabog","text_ar":"صَبْغ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabogap","text_ar":"صَبْغَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"baptism"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of their children in a sort of water that they have; (S; [and the like is said in the O, and Ksh, & c.;])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sbgp","text_ar":"صبغة"},{"kind":"text","text":"being in this instance in the accus. case as an objective complement; (Msb;) for the meaning is “ follow ye the religion of God; ” (O, Msb;) or “ we will follow the religion of God: ” (O:) or it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which God has prescribed"},{"kind":"text","text":"to Mohammad; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"circumcision:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sbgp","text_ar":"صبغة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in this instance an inf. n., (Ksh, Bd, Jel,) signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner of,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabog","text_ar":"صَبْغ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"baptism"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Ksh,) relating to the baptism of the Christians, (Ksh, Bd,) a corroborative of the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=man~aA","text_ar":"ا=مَنَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in verse 130], as such put in the accusative case, (Ksh, Bd, Jel,) by reason of a verb understood, (Jel,) the meaning being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaganaA A@ll~`hu Sibogatahu","text_ar":"صَبَغَنَا ا@للّٰهُ صِبْغَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God hath baptized us with his baptism"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Ksh, Bd, Jel; *) [so that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sibogapa A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"صِبْغَةَ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the baptism of God,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and may here be rendered We have received"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the baptism of God;;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the Muslims being hereby commanded to say to the Christians, “ Say ye, God hath baptized us ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaganaA","text_ar":"صَبَغَنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":") with the faith, with a baptism ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabogap","text_ar":"صَبْغَة"},{"kind":"text","text":") not like ours [i. e. not like our Christian baptism], and purified us with a purifying not like ours; ” or the Muslims being hereby commanded to say [of themselves], “ God hath baptized us ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaganaA","text_ar":"صَبَغَنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":") with the faith, as a baptism ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SibogapF","text_ar":"صِبْغَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"), and we have not been baptized with your baptism ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lamo nuSobago Sibogatakumo","text_ar":"لَمْ نُصْبَغْ صِبْغَتَكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"). ” (Ksh.)"}],"source_refs":["AA","O","K","TA","Msb","S","Ksh","Bd","Jel"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}